{"tid":1724341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑部電話俾人勾線","createTime":"2019-11-15T12:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T07:42:51.000Z","uid":200849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3b62a2ce4c8f433bf7fdd462717c715614de7ee3","tid":1724341,"uid":200849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"啱先有朋友打比我<br />\n我咩聲都聽唔到<br />\n佢再打黎 佢問我啱先講乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n佢：「你番黎未呀？」<br />\n有個男人：「等陣先，簽埋個兩張單」<br />\n仲有提及我住嘅地區嘅英文字母簡寫<br />\n佢：「喂？」<br />\n之後就收咗線了<br />\n<br />\n我用自由鳥<br />\n我唔知係勾線定好似以前個啲撘錯線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點先驗證到？<br />\n如果係 又應該點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我生性樂觀 唔自殺架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1224db62cd6b2233d94547dda432c3e44fec74","tid":1724341,"uid":123988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"我用中移，我都試過，近排<br />\n應該好多比人鈎左線"},{"pid":"69409ce18bdfd7ce2228f6222f0d508e2aa40f69","tid":1724341,"uid":200849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f1224db62cd6b2233d94547dda432c3e44fec74","tid":1724341,"uid":123988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"我用中移，我都試過，近排<br />\n應該好多比人鈎左線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲用中移"},{"pid":"f771ec75e180adae63d1adb068a76bf61053dce5","tid":1724341,"uid":200849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:53:04.000Z","msg":"屌 我懷疑示威區大部分都勾撚哂線"},{"pid":"6dccc6f782f5bb6c56cea24d9c3b38310a05917a","tid":1724341,"uid":200849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"屌，我通話紀錄都俾人改左<br />\n啱先2053 我無打過電話出去<br />\n我睇電話紀錄 我見到2053打咗俾我媽媽<br />\n我以為自己打錯<br />\n我放低咗電話<br />\n我突然想睇下我媽媽有無聽<br />\n我再㩒番入個通話紀錄就無咗了<br />\n<br />\n好不安<br />\n係我電話壞咗定咩"},{"pid":"ff373f825ed4fbe909d4ee0aa8863d3f0bcbc470","tid":1724341,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"即刻換電話號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108003021b3e0a1f69bbcaeb95fb169b52e616a9","tid":1724341,"uid":32515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 俾人勾線可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3ab581d517c684924106aac812681555b2e529","tid":1724341,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02eb8ad7f6bab783322dad1bbd7eb0563e6ee5c","tid":1724341,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"193a233446654c08ef678d39abf79fa77668097b","tid":1724341,"uid":123988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69409ce18bdfd7ce2228f6222f0d508e2aa40f69","tid":1724341,"uid":200849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f1224db62cd6b2233d94547dda432c3e44fec74","tid":1724341,"uid":123988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"我用中移，我都試過，近排<br />\n應該好多比人鈎左線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲用中移"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"呢件事之前岩岩簽，所以我而家將個電話打入冷宮<br />\n成日唔比網絡同wifi佢，根本半廢<br />\n<br />\n一定唔用黎傾電話<br />\n用就用whatsapp 電話"}]}